---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Complete Guide to Business Consultant Marketing Automation in Canada | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/professional-services/business-consultants" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Business Consultants
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-violet-100 text-violet-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Business Consultants</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">10 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          The Complete Guide to Business Consultant Marketing Automation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">
          Fill your project pipeline, nurture proposals, and build recurring engagement through automated lead systems.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
          
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8">
            Consulting is feast or famine. When you're deep in client work, marketing stops. Automation keeps your pipeline flowing even during your busiest engagements.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Thought Leadership That Runs Itself</h2>

          <p>
            Your expertise is your marketing. Automated content sequences—case studies, insights, frameworks—position you as the authority without daily effort. Prospects warm up while you focus on deliverables.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Proposal Follow-Up Without Being Pushy</h2>

          <p>
            Proposals go cold because follow-up feels awkward. Systematic sequences—value-add check-ins, case study shares, gentle deadline reminders—keep conversations alive professionally.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Past Clients Become Repeat Clients</h2>

          <p>
            Projects end and relationships go dormant. Automated reactivation sequences—check-ins, new service alerts, industry updates—nurture past clients into repeat engagements.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-600 to-purple-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Fill Your Pipeline?</h3>
            <p class="text-violet-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see exactly how we'd automate lead nurturing for your consulting practice.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white text-violet-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
